    NTSD_EAS, WILD_STOP_AT_DIR, WIN32_OEM, LARGE_FILE_SUPPORT,
    ZIP64_SUPPORT, and UNICODE_SUPPORT similar to how UnZip does.
    zip.c (Ed)
